{
  "texts": [
    "An HDT ontology model can be constructed based on ontology technology to provide a unified paradigm for the human body information-related data, which is expected to be an effective solution for data heterogeneity [92,93].",
    "• Real-time Interaction 5G technology helps HDT to address the problem of real-time interaction because the development of 5G \\6G networks has added the additional potential for precise real-time data collection and access [94].",
    "Due to its highly reliable connection, high speed and low latency, 5G systems have been widely applied and deployed in various countries [95].",
    "5G is the critical technology for realizing real-time remote interaction.",
    "Various experimental verifications show that the 5G video transmission delay is 49ms, which well meets the needs of real-time interaction for low delay."
  ]
}